{"tid":185644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"21歲少女墮樓喪命 母親激動送院","createTime":"2017-04-03T15:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T23:15:06.000Z","uid":51904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a42804c550c006af23cea7b3fb356015e4d46f","tid":185644,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:14:46.000Z","msg":"【20:20 更新】墮樓少女抵院後不治<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳厚德邨德裕樓，傍晚近6時，一名年約21歲少女由高處墮下，重傷倒卧平台，街坊見狀報案。救護員接報到場，將墮樓少女送院搶救，抵院後證實不治。警員尋獲少女的母親，她得悉女兒墮樓後情緒激動，須送院檢查。警方正調查其墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"c8f1f2966481680c70a5c4d16df94ef39169a87e","tid":185644,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T17:12:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62a7685d9f000bccf24e7a28f7309c81c42ce648","tid":185644,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T17:15:18.000Z","msg":"124"},{"pid":"0a7edb5c0a097ed501464cb0588cf8541275c72a","tid":185644,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T17:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbebd47476816b0b6e6a60b963a0426f2f204ab9","tid":185644,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T20:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港地有塊西咁著數都自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n塊西可以當八達通嘟就話姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a48034f566dfc64290be5dcb7862b15dc9a442","tid":185644,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T20:49:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港地有塊西咁著數都自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n塊西可以當八達通嘟就話姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class